<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 14:04:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列和加沙战争升级到底意味着什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/what-does-the-escalation-of-the-israel-gaza-war-really-mean/0000018b-60cc-d8e2-a1eb-e3de165c0000</link><description>媒体充斥着“垂直升级”和“水平升级”等词语，但它们在以色列、加沙、真主党和伊朗的背景下到底意味着什么 — — 以及为什么美国如此担心？</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 13:52:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/what-does-the-escalation-of-the-israel-gaza-war-really-mean/0000018b-60cc-d8e2-a1eb-e3de165c0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列基本上是在告诉其公民‘你需要照顾好自己’”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-basically-telling-citizens-you-need-to-take-care-of-yourself/0000018b-6180-d312-a1fb-f7fb54730000</link><description>以色列国内军备竞赛将如何影响其未来？哈马斯野蛮袭击后规则放松，以色列持枪人数将增加两倍</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 13:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-basically-telling-citizens-you-need-to-take-care-of-yourself/0000018b-6180-d312-a1fb-f7fb54730000</guid></item><item><title>我想对国际左派说的是——见鬼去吧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/all-i-want-to-say-to-the-international-left-is-go-to-hell/0000018b-6196-d473-a5fb-65dfce6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 12:27:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/all-i-want-to-say-to-the-international-left-is-go-to-hell/0000018b-6196-d473-a5fb-65dfce6b0000</guid></item><item><title>好莱坞一线明星请愿拜登采取行动从加沙解救以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/hollywood-a-listers-petition-biden-to-take-action-to-free-israeli-hostages-from-hamas/0000018b-616a-d473-a5fb-65eb4df90000</link><description>包括布莱德利·库珀、格温妮丝·帕特洛和贾斯汀·汀布莱克在内的数十名名人对加沙的 220 多名人质表示“极度担忧”。信中写道：“他们在 10 月 7 日的野蛮屠杀中被哈马斯俘虏，1400 多名以色列人被屠杀。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 12:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/hollywood-a-listers-petition-biden-to-take-action-to-free-israeli-hostages-from-hamas/0000018b-616a-d473-a5fb-65eb4df90000</guid></item><item><title>为什么世界媒体相信哈马斯关于加沙医院爆炸的骗局？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-did-the-world-media-believe-the-hamas-hoax-about-the-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-5c6d-d00f-a9bf-7c7dd2d40000</link><description>哈马斯管理的加沙卫生部就像奥威尔式的“真理部”一样可靠。但这并没有阻止世界各地的记者争先恐后地放大恐怖组织的说法，即阿赫利医院的爆炸是以色列的空袭</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 11:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-did-the-world-media-believe-the-hamas-hoax-about-the-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-5c6d-d00f-a9bf-7c7dd2d40000</guid></item><item><title>由于限制越来越多，以色列军队将巴勒斯坦活动人士驱逐出希伯伦的家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expels-palestinian-activist-from-hebron-home-amid-increasing-restrictions/0000018b-6129-d307-adbb-6539a3aa0000</link><description>以色列国防军士兵要求伊萨·阿姆罗在战争期间离开他位于该市以色列控制区的家。居住在希伯伦该地区的其他巴勒斯坦人表示，由于以色列国防军试图控制该市的行动，实际上“完全禁止外出”</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 11:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expels-palestinian-activist-from-hebron-home-amid-increasing-restrictions/0000018b-6129-d307-adbb-6539a3aa0000</guid></item><item><title>现已获释的以色列祖母讲述了哈马斯被囚禁的经历，称“政府抛弃了我们”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/85-year-old-israeli-grandmother-recounts-hamas-captivity-says-government-deserted-us/0000018b-615d-d312-a1fb-f77f9aea0000</link><description>85 岁的 Yocheved Lifshitz 是周一晚些时候获释的两名妇女之一，大约 220 名人质仍留在哈马斯手中。在特拉维夫一家医院，她揭露了哈马斯的加沙地道、医疗情况，并讲述了10月7日的暴力绑架事件</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 11:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/85-year-old-israeli-grandmother-recounts-hamas-captivity-says-government-deserted-us/0000018b-615d-d312-a1fb-f77f9aea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方逮捕一名涉嫌支持哈马斯袭击的女演员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-actress-over-online-post-allegedly-endorsing-hamas-attack/0000018b-612c-d307-adbb-653c3fd00000</link><description>梅萨·阿卜杜勒·哈迪 (Maisa Abd Elhadi) 被捕之前，国家检察官正式支持审判任何赞扬哈马斯在以色列南部犯下暴行的人</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 10:52:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-actress-over-online-post-allegedly-endorsing-hamas-attack/0000018b-612c-d307-adbb-653c3fd00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的部长们希望“把他的头放在盘子上”，但拒绝公开这么说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ministers-desire-to-put-his-head-on-a-platter-refuse-to-say-so-openly/0000018b-60f1-d2b2-addf-66f9e33a0000</link><description>经过 17 天的战争后，利库德集团部长们加大了对内塔尼亚胡的攻击力度，但并不准备辞职。具有讽刺意味的是，由甘茨和艾森科特组成的战时内阁从利库德集团那里获得的支持比原来的内阁要多得多</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 10:44:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ministers-desire-to-put-his-head-on-a-platter-refuse-to-say-so-openly/0000018b-60f1-d2b2-addf-66f9e33a0000</guid></item><item><title>火箭弹袭击以色列中部和南部；内塔尼亚胡告诉马克龙：“哈马斯是新纳粹”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-live/two-elderly-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-frances-macron-to-visit-israel-ramallah/0000018b-5f5d-d2b2-addf-7f7dcd790000</link><description>法国总统马克龙抵达以色列，会见内塔尼亚胡、赫尔佐格、人质家属和巴勒斯坦权力机构主席阿巴斯 ■ 两名从哈马斯囚禁中获释的老年妇女 ■ 内塔尼亚胡和拜登发表讲话，白宫表示“现在不是停火的时候” ■ 至少 1,300 人死亡自 10 月 7 日起由哈马斯控制 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：5,300 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，18,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 09:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article-live/two-elderly-israeli-hostages-freed-from-gaza-frances-macron-to-visit-israel-ramallah/0000018b-5f5d-d2b2-addf-7f7dcd790000</guid></item><item><title>亲爱的 BLM 活动人士，我们以色列人也无法呼吸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/dear-blm-activists-we-israelis-also-cant-breathe/0000018b-5d91-d8e2-a1eb-ff97f7c00000</link><description>让我告诉你一些关于以色列的事情，那里的犹太人大部分是来自阿拉伯国家和北非的棕色人种</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 08:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/dear-blm-activists-we-israelis-also-cant-breathe/0000018b-5d91-d8e2-a1eb-ff97f7c00000</guid></item><item><title>开源情报显示美国向以色列、塞浦路斯和约旦部署了更多武器和军队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-24/ty-article/u-s-deploys-more-arms-and-troops-to-israel-cyprus-and-jordan/0000018b-5cbf-d307-adbb-7dbf1aa80000</link><description>近80架美国军用飞机和数十架租赁民用飞机正在运输设备，向以色列和塞浦路斯空运大量武器，向约旦空运战斗机中队和特种部队</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 08:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-24/ty-article/u-s-deploys-more-arms-and-troops-to-israel-cyprus-and-jordan/0000018b-5cbf-d307-adbb-7dbf1aa80000</guid></item><item><title>在黎巴嫩，平民听到以色列的战争威胁，但无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/in-lebanon-civilians-hear-israeli-threats-of-war-but-have-nowhere-to-turn/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff3622b20000</link><description>对于因预期以色列和真主党之间的冲突升级而逃离黎巴嫩南部的平民来说，贝鲁特缺乏正常运作的政府使生活变得更加困难</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/in-lebanon-civilians-hear-israeli-threats-of-war-but-have-nowhere-to-turn/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff3622b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙地面进攻之前进行了一场令人紧张的等待游戏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</link><description>加沙地面行动的拖延加剧了政府与军队之间以及政府内部的信任危机 ■ 在释放两名以色列老年妇女后，哈马斯希望部分释放人质能够减轻其面临的国际压力在下面</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</guid></item><item><title>人质母亲：“以色列必须非常小心，避免造成我们无法挽回的伤害”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 22:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的首要任务必须是释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-top-priority-must-be-to-free-the-hostages/0000018b-5e35-d473-a5fb-7efd82530000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 21:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/israels-top-priority-must-be-to-free-the-hostages/0000018b-5e35-d473-a5fb-7efd82530000</guid></item><item><title>不要让对哈马斯报仇的呼声压制我们的良心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-let-calls-for-revenge-against-hamas-silence-our-conscience/0000018b-5d90-d8e2-a1eb-ff966bca0000</link><descrip